I can expose the `proxy` variable which you can set in the Gruntfile with a proxy setting:

```
topcoat: {
            download: {
                options: {
                    srcPath: 'tmp/src/',
                    repos: '<%= pkg.topcoat %>',
                    proxy: 'http://uid:pw@proxy.domain.tld'
